units metal
atom_style atomic
boundary p p p
read_data data.h2

pair_style allegro
pair_coeff * * /opt/phal/probes/md/allegro-probe.nequip.pth H

neighbor 1.0 bin
neigh_modify every 1 delay 0 check yes

velocity all create 1.0 20251103 mom yes rot no dist gaussian
fix integrate all nve
timestep 0.0001

thermo 1
thermo_style custom step temp pe ke etotal
run 10
